inair.view

Class UILayeredNavigationView

  • java.lang.Object
    • inair.data.DependencyObject
      • inair.data.IAElement
        • inair.input.IAInputElement
          • inair.view.UIView
            • inair.view.UIViewGroup
              • inair.view.UIAbstractCollectionView
                • inair.view.UILayeredNavigationView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UIViewManager, UIViewParent

    public final class UILayeredNavigationView
extends UIAbstractCollectionView

    Layout manager that allows the user to flip near and far through pages of data.

     Attribute for UILayeredNavigationView can use in layout xml file

 And all attribute can use with UIAbstractCollectionView

    Note this class is currently under early design and development. The API will likely change in later updates of the compatibility library, requiring changes to the source code of apps when they are compiled against the newer version.
